---
title: Chicken, Veggie Gyozas & Sesame Potato Fries with Asian Slaw & Japanese Sauce
description: Gyozas have so much variety to them that deciding on one is tricky. Let’s kick things off with these chicken and veggie-loaded parcels that are folded into delicate little presents. A Japanese dressing will hit the spot as a saucy accompaniment.
